---
title: Seared Italian Sausages with Veggie Succotash
description: Orzo pasta is perfect for soups and salads. In this warm salad, sausage serves as the ultimate flavour bomb and carrots, zucchini and bell peppers create a fresh and colourful presentation. We finished it with a fresh squeeze of lemon to brighten the flavours.
